                            <comment id="13032707" author="pbruski_" created="Thu, 12 May 2011 22:07:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve encountered the problem on OS X and AMQ 5.4.2, but it looks like the issue is still present in trunk.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13059084" author="tabish121" created="Sat, 2 Jul 2011 16:39:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Verified that the queue is not protected and the read lock around that code is not needed once the code is switched to a ConcurrentLinkQueue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Nice catch, thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
